                <h2>Dane Anthony Bands</h2>
                <p>This versatile core group of five accomplished musicians are Atlantic City lounge legends! They can make you sing, dance and clap your hands to the ‘boogity’ beat whether it’s pop, rock, blues, or R&B (and sometimes a little bit country).  Whatever your favorite genre, this band can cover it in their own unique style, put a smile on your face, and surely start a party!</p>
